022import java.lang.annotation.Retention;

025

027 * Used to specify a key for an {@link EnhancedHashMap}.

029 * @author creatorfromhell
030 * @see EnhancedHashMap
031 * @since 0.1.2.0
032 */
033
034@Target(ElementType.METHOD)

037}
